    <item>
      <title>工党在竞选捐款方面领先英国保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国两个反对党报告称，他们获得的捐款金额超过了首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党在大选竞选第二周筹集的捐款金额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚与俄罗斯边境设置界线 暂停通行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lines-at-border-with-russia-leave-estonia-mulling-halt-to-travel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚表示，将于周末关闭这个波罗的海国家前往俄罗斯的主要航线，称边境长队对健康和公共秩序构成了威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lines-at-border-with-russia-leave-estonia-mulling-halt-to-travel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 10:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京与金正恩的防御协议引起美国及其盟友的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/putin-s-rare-trip-to-asian-security-partners-pays-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京的亚洲之行为他赢得了支持，使他能够继续对乌克兰发动残酷的战争，同时也引起了美国及其盟友韩国的警惕，韩国目前正考虑向基辅提供可能改变战场形势的武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/putin-s-rare-trip-to-asian-security-partners-pays-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部撤销对 TikTok 误导美国消费者的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/doj-drops-tiktok-claims-raised-by-ftc-over-misleading-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部撤销了针对字节跳动有限公司旗下 TikTok 的两项拟议指控之一，计划在今年晚些时候将消费者保护诉讼的重点放在儿童隐私上，而不是指控该视频共享平台在数据安全方面误导消费者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/doj-drops-tiktok-claims-raised-by-ftc-over-misleading-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
